'''Custódia''' is a city in the state of [[Pernambuco]], [[Brazil]]. The population in 2009, according with [[Brazilian Institute of Geography and Statistics|IBGE]] was 33.874 inhabitants and the total area is 1404.1&nbsp;km².
==Geography==
* State - [[Pernambuco]] * Region - [[Sertão]] Pernambucano * Boundaries - [[Iguaraci]] and [[Carnaíba]] ('''N'''); [[Floresta, Pernambuco|Floresta]] and [[Ibimirim]] ('''S'''); [[Sertânia]] ('''E'''); [[Betânia, Pernambuco|Betânia]] and [[Flores, Pernambuco|Flores]] ('''W'''). * Area - 1404.1&nbsp;km² * Elevation - 542 m * Hidrography - [[Pajeú River|Pajeú]] and [[Moxotó River|Moxotó rivers]] * Vegetation - [[Caatinga]] [[hiperxerófila]] * Clima - [[semi arid]] - ([[Sertão]]) hot * Annual average temperature - 24.0 c * Distance to [[Recife]] - 334.4&nbsp;km
==Economy==
The main economic activities in '''Custódia''' are based in food & beverage industry, commerce and [[agribusiness]], especially creation of [[goat]]s, [[sheep]], [[cattle]], [[pigs]], [[horse]]s, [[chicken]]s; and plantations of [[onion]]s, [[bean]]s and [[tomato]]es.
